<h2>Partnership {{#if accepted}}Accepted{{else}}Declined{{/if}}</h2>

<p>Hello,</p>

<p>Your partnership request to <strong>{{target_company_name}}</strong> has been <strong>{{#if accepted}}accepted{{else}}declined{{/if}}</strong>.</p>

{{#if accepted}}
<p>You can now:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Share jobs with {{target_company_name}}</li>
  <li>Set up auto-assignment rules</li>
  <li>Collaborate on service coverage</li>
</ul>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{partners_url}}" class="button">View Partners</a>
</p>
{{else}}
{{#if decline_reason}}
<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{decline_reason}}</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #64748b;">
  You can send partnership requests to other companies from the Directory.
</p>
{{/if}}
